        <p class="lead">We are looking for strong, professional English teachers who can deliver high-quality live Zoom lessons to ambitious students and professionals.</p>
        <p class="sub">Instead of filling in a cold form, applicants can complete a guided chat-style application. The assistant asks one question at a time, keeps the process simple, and submits everything directly by email.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="#teacherAssistant" class="btn btn-primary">Start Application</a>
